#~ "<ulink url=\"http://doc.qt.nokia.com/latest/qt.html#Key-enum\">Qt "
#~ "dokumentatsioonis</ulink>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Developing a command line script requires to reload the scripts to see "
#~ "whether the changes behave appropriately. Instead of restarting the "
